ZH: 这座小桥就是两个省份的疆界。
EN: This small bridge marks the border between two provinces.

ZH: 这条河流是国家的疆界。
EN: This river serves as the national border.

ZH: 疆界问题一直是两国之间的争议焦点。
EN: Border issues have always been a contentious point between the two countries.

ZH: 这座山脉是两个国家的疆界。
EN: This mountain range forms the border between two countries.

ZH: 疆界线已经被画在地图上。
EN: The border lines have been marked on the map.

ZH: 这些标志物表示了双方的疆界。
EN: These markers indicate the boundaries between the two sides.

ZH: 这是我们国家的疆界之外。
EN: This is beyond the border of our country.

ZH: 他们已经越过了这个疆界。
EN: They have crossed over the border.

ZH: 请不要越过这个疆界。
EN: Please do not cross this boundary.

ZH: 疆界周围设置了警示标志。
EN: Warning signs are placed around the border.

ZH: 这个疆界地区属于军事管制地带。
EN: This border area is under military control.

ZH: 他们住在疆界的对面。
EN: They live on the other side of the border.

ZH: 这里有一个不断变化的疆界。
EN: The border here is constantly changing.

ZH: 美国和加拿大之间有一个长长的疆界。
EN: There is a long border between the United States and Canada.

ZH: 这片土地上有一条虚拟的疆界。
EN: There is a virtual border on this piece of land.

ZH: 疆界问题需要通过外交途径解决。
EN: Border issues need to be resolved through diplomatic channels.

ZH: 我们应该尊重对方国家的疆界。
EN: We should respect the borders of other countries.

ZH: 这里是两个省份的交界处。
EN: This is the border between two provinces.

ZH: 这个小岛是两国的疆界争端焦点。
EN: This small island is at the center of a border dispute between two countries.

ZH: 在这条河的边缘就是两国的疆界。
EN: The border between the two countries lies at the edge of this river.
